Yeah.

01:25.785 --> 01:29.689
I-i-i've gained
A belt size i'm aware of
With anticipation bingeing.

01:32.659 --> 01:35.528
Greg, can you excuse me
Just for a second?
Oh, yeah, sure. Sorry.

01:35.528 --> 01:38.465
Hey, greg. I thought
You were startin' a diet.

01:38.465 --> 01:40.467
Yeah. At 8:00 a.m.

01:40.467 --> 01:43.470
That-that-that's
My farewell doughnut.
