01:43.470 --> 01:46.639
This is detective simone.
I was just wondering
If that--

01:46.639 --> 01:49.542
Oh, yeah, yeah.
It did, huh? Okay.

01:49.542 --> 01:51.978
So, i'll, uh-- i'll be
Around to pick it up
Around lunchtime.

01:51.978 --> 01:54.781
Uh-huh. Right.

01:55.281 --> 01:58.518
The balance is, uh,
Twenty-eight hundred, fifty.

01:58.518 --> 02:01.387
Okay. Yeah. All right.
See you then.
Holy cow.

02:03.022 --> 02:05.592
One-- one second.
Fifteen squad.
Good morning.

02:05.592 --> 02:07.827
- good morning. Can i help you?
- yeah, uh--
-[ simone ] lieu.

02:08.360 --> 02:10.697
Yeah, mornin', lieu.
Any chance you might be
The new p.a.a.?

02:10.697 --> 02:12.432
Gina colon.
Transferred from the borough.

02:12.866 --> 02:15.034
Hi. James martinez.
I'm a detective
In the squad.

02:15.401 --> 02:17.737
Is this the anticrime unit?
Nah. It's upstairs.

02:17.737 --> 02:19.973
That's where you been
Assigned to?
Oh. Yeah, uh-huh.

02:19.973 --> 02:23.676
We're expectin' a new p.a.a.
Also. I thought, you know,
Maybe it was you.

02:23.676 --> 02:27.514
Well, thanks for the directions.
One flight up. Sure.

02:27.514 --> 02:29.516
Hey.
Hey, andy.

02:31.518 --> 02:33.353
How's it goin'?
[ simone ]
What's doin', andy?

02:33.353 --> 02:36.422
- did you, uh--
  Did you get that thing?
- pickin' it up lunchtime.

02:36.723 --> 02:39.826
- hey, andy.
  All set for the weigh-in?
-no.

02:40.226 --> 02:42.529
-andy.
- i'm not startin'
  A diet today, medavoy.

02:42.529 --> 02:44.464
-[ fancy ] homicide.
- i'm up.

02:44.464 --> 02:48.168
Okay. D.o.a. By the bridge.
Take the squad for canvass.

02:48.601 --> 02:51.704
This has become
A nightmare, andy--
These continual postponements.

02:51.704 --> 02:54.674
I'm not startin' a diet today.
You wanna start it,
You start it yourself.

02:55.074 --> 02:57.076
Andy, we both require
Peer reinforcement.

02:57.076 --> 02:58.945
We've discussed this.
Medavoy, shut up.

02:59.245 --> 03:01.681
- excuse me. Is this
  The 15th detective squad?
- yes.

03:01.681 --> 03:04.884
Hi. I'm geri turner.
I'm your new p.a.a.

03:04.884 --> 03:08.021
You'll wanna see
Lieutenant fancy.
Thank you.

03:12.992 --> 03:16.329
Where'd you disappear so early?
I had to make
A couple of calls.

03:26.406 --> 03:28.374
[ chatter on police radio ]

03:28.808 --> 03:31.644
So, uh, she got no inkling--
Russell?

03:31.644 --> 03:33.913
