03:40.420 --> 03:43.156
You don't wanna start
On that diet today, huh?
No.

03:43.156 --> 03:45.158
We're gonna have to start
Moving greg around
On a handcart.

03:45.658 --> 03:47.660
[ sipowicz ]
So, what have we got?

03:48.127 --> 03:50.496
We got a black male,
Looks about 50. Shot
Three times in the chest.

03:50.830 --> 03:54.334
That's the guy
Who found him--
Arnold cassell.

03:54.334 --> 03:57.270
He didn't happen to see
Who dropped it off?
No.

03:57.670 --> 04:00.106
[ man on p.a., indistinct ]
[ simone ]
Excuse me.

04:00.473 --> 04:02.842
I'm detective simone.
What can you tell us
About what happened here?

04:02.842 --> 04:06.246
I was out with my dog,
And then he started
To urinate on the trunk,

04:06.246 --> 04:09.182
And then suddenly
He got very agitated.

04:09.182 --> 04:11.884
[ dog whining ]
He was pawing at it
And whimpering.

04:12.185 --> 04:14.687
Look at him. Please.
He's still very agitated.
It's okay.

04:15.188 --> 04:16.689
Sir? That's when
You looked inside--

04:17.156 --> 04:19.791
I looked inside,
And then i saw the body.

04:20.293 --> 04:22.795
And, uh, then of course
I called 911.

04:22.795 --> 04:25.932
- that trunk was moved.
- all right.
  Thanks a lot, mr. Cassell.

04:26.332 --> 04:28.935
You see them drag marks?
That trunk got dumped
Over here...

04:28.935 --> 04:30.937
And moved by hand
Over there.

04:30.937 --> 04:34.374
- you see those humps over here?
- that's bauman and giamatti
  From the 13th.

04:34.874 --> 04:36.442
You can make book
That they're the ones
That moved it.

04:36.843 --> 04:40.847
- what do you got, andy?
- we got a dump job, bauman--
  30 feet into our precinct.

04:40.847 --> 04:43.850
- i'll start the canvass.
- yeah. Lots of luck.

04:43.850 --> 04:46.886
[ simone ] excuse me.
Is that a body
In that trunk, sip?

04:47.220 --> 04:48.821
Don't ask me what's
In the trunk again.

04:48.821 --> 04:50.790
Some lucky break
For you guys, huh, bauman?
[ horn honks ]

04:51.190 --> 04:52.992
[ brakes squealing ]
It got dragged clear out
Of your jurisdiction.

04:53.226 --> 04:56.329
-[ giamatti ]
 We resent that inference.
- [ no audible dialogue ]

04:56.329 --> 04:58.898
You just lost yourselves help
Canvassing all these witnesses.

04:58.898 --> 05:00.900
Oh, now that's
A laugh riot, bauman.

05:00.900 --> 05:02.902
You keep crackin' wise,
I'll put you in there
With the stiff.

05:03.403 --> 05:06.239
He got no i.d.
The bottom of the trunk
Is lined with the sundaypost.

05:06.539 --> 05:09.475
All right. How about this?
This driver saw the trunk
Dumped,

05:09.475 --> 05:11.644
And he saw it loaded
Onto a van on 14th street.

05:11.878 --> 05:14.714
[ driver ]
Fourteenth and avenue "c."
How likely is that--

05:15.048 --> 05:17.183
To see the thing get
Picked up and dumped off
On the same bus run?

05:17.183 --> 05:19.552
Can you tell us anything
About the people who did it?
[ siren wails ]

05:19.552 --> 05:23.823
Two black guys, average height.
Looked like they were
In their 20s.

05:23.823 --> 05:27.593
It was a beat-up chevy van--
Light brown, no plates.

05:27.593 --> 05:30.963
I got his pedigree.
Thanks a lot for stoppin'.

05:31.397 --> 05:34.233
- yeah, it was stop
  Or run her over.
- thanks. Appreciate it.

05:34.567 --> 05:36.936
- bobby, here's a couple photos
  From the d.o.a.
- yeah.

05:37.270 --> 05:39.205
What do you say
If we actually
Clear this case, huh?

05:39.572 --> 05:41.941
You guys wanna take a ride
With us over to 14th street?
Maybe we can make an i.d.

05:42.241 --> 05:45.078
- nah.
- you got it covered.

05:45.078 --> 05:47.013
They're still workin' off
The lord's instructions--

05:47.013 --> 05:49.949
Do nothing
Till i return to earth.

05:49.949 --> 05:52.018
You puttin' on
A little weight,
Medavoy?

05:52.118 --> 05:54.987
Kiss my ass, giamatti.
Give it a big smooch.

07:05.224 --> 07:06.626
?? Hey ??

